title: Brother P touch D600 Labelling Machine with PC connection
description:
The P-touch D600VP creates durable, fade-proof labels by using the easy-to-use integrated labelling functions, or directly from your PC or Mac thanks to the fully-featured P-touch Editor label design software.
 
A large colour LCD display with label preview function, and a wide PC-style keyboard make it easy to quickly produce your labels in various colour and size combinations thanks to its high-speed print capabilities and fully automatic cutter.
